text: jongok is a locality situated in Luleå Municipality, Norrbotten County, Sweden with 839 inhabitants in 2010. Rutwik also 'Rutvik' is an Indian boy name which is a title for the one who possess the knowledge of all the four Vedas. Usually the high priest of a Hindu temple or saint. Also, Rutmik (रुत्मिक) which is an Indian boy name derived from Sanskrit language means teacher of saints, the one who is guru of Rutvik. == References == Category:Populated places in Luleå Municipality Category:Norrbotten
title: Rutvik
